      • stringToParameterMap

        public static StreamParametersMapFunction<String> stringToParameterMap(Class<?> testClass)
        Start building a Parameter Mapper function, assuming that the input are String, and using the type of the @Parameter field.

        Fields not supported will not be mapped and must be handled manually, using andMap method.

        Parameters:
        testClass - the testClass with the annotation
        Returns:
        the function on the parameter array
